$lang['privacy_32']	= "這為私隱政策是什麼？";//"What is this Privacy Policy for?";
$lang['privacy_1']	= "本私隱政策是為此網站 [www.tcsp.org] 和由南菲律賓臺灣商會服務並控制其使用者選擇使用它的人的隱私。該策略設置了使用者的隱私非常關注，並概述了使用者，網站和網站擁有者的義務要求的不同領域。此外本網站處理、 存儲和保護使用者資料和資訊的方式也將在此政策範圍內詳細說明。";//"This privacy policy is for this website [www.tcsp.org] and served by Taiwanese Chamber of the South Philippines and governs the privacy of its users who choose to use it. The policy sets out the different areas where user privacy is concerned and outlines the obligations & requirements of the users, the website and website owners. Furthermore the way this website processes, stores and protects user data and information will also be detailed within this policy.";
$lang['privacy_2']	= "網站";//"The Website";
$lang['privacy_3']	= "本網站和它的擁有者採取主動的做法，對使用者的隱私，並確保採取必要的步驟，以保護其整個他們參觀體驗的使用者的隱私。本網站遵守的所有英國國家法律和使用者隱私的要求。";//"This website and it's owners take a proactive approach to user privacy and ensure the necessary steps are taken to protect the privacy of its users throughout their visiting experience. This website comply's to all UK national laws and requirements for user privacy.";
$lang['privacy_4']	= "使用“餅干”技術";//"Use of Cookies";
$lang['privacy_5']	= "本網站使用 cookie 來更好的使用者體驗，同時訪問該網站。在適用的情況下本網站使用 cookie 控制系統，從而允許使用者在他們第一次訪問網站上允許或不允許在其電腦上的 cookie 的使用 / 設備。這是符合最近的立法要求對網站的明確同意從使用者獲取之前留下或讀取 cookie 等使用者電腦上的檔 / 設備。";//"This website uses cookies to better the users experience while visiting the website. Where applicable this website uses a cookie control system allowing the user on their first visit to the website to allow or disallow the use of cookies on their computer / device. This complies with recent legislation requirements for website's to obtain explicit consent from users before leaving behind or reading files such as cookies on a users computer / device.";
$lang['privacy_6']	= "Cookie 是保存到使用者電腦硬碟上的小檔，跟蹤、 保存和存儲有關使用者的交互和使用本網站的資訊。這將允許的網站，通過它的伺服器，為使用者提供量身定做的經驗在本網站內。如果他們想要拒絕的使用和保存的 cookie 從本網站到他們的電腦硬碟上他們應採取必要步驟內其 web 瀏覽器的安全設置，以阻止所有 cookie 從本網站和它是外部服務供應商建議使用者。";//"Cookies are small files saved to the users computers hard drive that track, save and store information about the users interactions and usage of the website. This allows the website, through it's server to provide the users with a tailored experience within this website. Users are advised that if they wish to deny the use and saving of cookies from this website on to their computers hard drive they should take necessary steps within their web browsers security settings to block all cookies from this website and it's external serving vendors.";
$lang['privacy_7']	= "本網站使用跟蹤軟體來監視它的遊客更好地瞭解他們是如何使用它。該軟體提供的 Google Analytics 使用 cookie 來跟蹤訪客使用。該軟體會將 cookie 保存到電腦硬碟上跟蹤和監視您的參與和使用本網站，但將不存儲、 保存或收集的個人資訊。您可以閱讀谷歌的私隱政策在這裡進一步資訊 [HTTP://www.google.com/privacy.html]。";//"This website uses tracking software to monitor it's visitors to better understand how they use it. This software is provided by Google Analytics which uses cookies to track visitor usage. The software will save a cookie to your computers hard drive in order to track and monitor your engagement and usage of the website but will not store, save or collect personal information. You can read Google's privacy policy here for further information [ http://www.google.com/privacy.html ].";
$lang['privacy_8']	= "其他餅乾可能存儲到電腦硬碟上由外部供應商在本網站使用轉診程式時，贊助連結或廣告。這種 cookie 用於轉換和跟蹤的轉診和通常過期 30 天后，雖然有些可能更長。存儲、 保存或收集的個人資訊。";//"Other cookies may be stored to your computers hard drive by external vendors when this website uses referral programs, sponsored links or adverts. Such cookies are used for conversion and referral tracking and typically expire after 30 days, though some may take longer. No personal information is stored, saved or collected.";
$lang['privacy_9']	= "聯絡&通訊";//"Contact & Communication";
