$lang['privacy_12']	= "電子郵件電子報";//"Email Newsletter";
$lang['privacy_13']	= "本網站設有一個電子郵件通訊方案,用於向用戶提供產品和服務由本網站。 用戶可以通過一個在線訂閱自動化進程應他們想這樣做,但這樣做,在他們自己的判斷。 一些訂閱可手動處理通過事先書面同意的用戶。";//"This website operates an email newsletter program, used to inform subscribers about products and services supplied by this website. Users can subscribe through an online automated process should they wish to do so but do so at their own discretion. Some subscriptions may be manually processed through prior written agreement with the user.";
