$lang['privacy_26']	= "本網站可能使用社會分享按鈕的説明分享到社交媒體平臺問題直接從 web 頁的 web 內容。建議使用者在使用這種社會的共用按鈕，他們這樣做在他們自己的謹慎和注意的社交媒體平臺可能會跟蹤和保存您的請求以共用 web 頁分別通過您的社交媒體平臺帳戶之前。";//"This website may use social sharing buttons which help share web content directly from web pages to the social media platform in question. Users are advised before using such social sharing buttons that they do so at their own discretion and note that the social media platform may track and save your request to share a web page respectively through your social media platform account.";
